descr: "This resource allows for the definition of various types of plans as a sharable, consumable, and executable artifact. The resource is general enough to support the description of a broad range of clinical artifacts such as clinical decision support rules, order sets and protocols."

fields.name: measure
fields.descr: "The parameter whose value is to be tracked, e.g. body weigth, blood pressure, or hemoglobin A1c level."

fields.name: detailQuantity
fields.descr: "The target value of the measure to be achieved to signify fulfillment of the goal, e.g. 150 pounds or 7.0%. Either the high or low or both values of the range can be specified. Whan a low value is missing, it indicates that the goal is achieved at any value at or below the high value. Similarly, if the high value is missing, it indicates that the goal is achieved at any value at or above the low value."

fields.name: due
